description: High-performance laptop with 15-inch display, Intel i7 processor, 16GB RAM, and 512GB SSD. Perfect for professional work and gaming.
Ergonomic wireless mouse with 6 programmable buttons, 2400 DPI optical sensor, and long battery life. Compatible with Windows and Mac.
7-in-1 USB-C hub with HDMI, USB 3.0 ports, SD card reader, and USB-C power delivery. Ideal for laptops and tablets.
RGB mechanical keyboard with Cherry MX switches, customizable backlighting, and programmable macro keys. Great for typing and gaming.
4K UHD monitor with 27-inch IPS panel, HDR support, and 99% sRGB color accuracy. Perfect for content creation and entertainment.
1080p HD webcam with auto-focus, built-in microphone, and low-light correction. Ideal for video conferencing and streaming.
Adjustable aluminum laptop stand with ergonomic design, cooling ventilation, and non-slip rubber pads. Supports laptops up to 17 inches.
Portable external SSD with 1TB storage, USB 3.1 Gen 2 interface, and transfer speeds up to 540MB/s. Compact and durable design.
Over-ear headphones with active noise cancellation, 30-hour battery life, and premium sound quality. Foldable design with travel case.
Digital drawing tablet with 8192 pressure levels, battery-free pen, and customizable express keys. Compatible with major design software.
LED desk lamp with adjustable brightness, color temperature control, and USB charging port. Energy-efficient and eye-friendly.
Cable management set including cable clips, sleeves, and ties. Keeps your workspace organized and tidy.
High-capacity portable charger with dual USB ports, fast charging support, and LED power indicator. Charges smartphones up to 4 times.
Portable Bluetooth speaker with 360-degree sound, waterproof design, and 12-hour battery life. Perfect for outdoor activities.
Anti-theft laptop backpack with padded compartment for 15.6-inch laptops, USB charging port, and multiple organizational pockets.
